tagline: Welcome to my personal web page.
body:
Hello! I'm

Binod Bastakoti

. Full Stack Developer specializing in back end development. Experienced with all stages of the development cycle for dynamic web projects. Innovative and enthusiastic software engineer. Having experience in advanced Java programming to develop web-based and mobile applications. Demonstrated abilities in user interface (UI) development, database management, and technical reporting. Agile problem solver, taking a proactive approach to testing, troubleshooting, identify issues, and thorough debugging. Adept at collaborating to integrate diverse modules. Solid contributor on all phases of software development life cycle (SDLC). Well-versed in numerous programming languages including AngularJs, JavaScript, SQL, and C. Strong background in project management and customer relations.
